<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONSEQUENCES OF PORNOGRAPHY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We were delighted to see the article on the social impact of illegal 
pornography. Just as the community has united on the war against drugs, we must 
also join together to eradicate illegal pornography which debases our women and 
children, and contributes to a wide variety of violent crimes. 
</P>
<P>
Because we believe that one of the most urgent causes today is the more 
stringent enforcement of existing laws against illegal (child and violent) 
pornography, we implore our local law enforcement agencies and the U.S. 
attorney's office to prosecute those who have broken these laws. 
</P>
<P>
JOANNE GALLAGHER 
</P>
<P>
JOE GALLAGHER 
</P>
<P>
Sherman Oaks 
</P>
</TEXT>
