</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
56 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
SMALL TO FORGO BASKETBALL SEASON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Errol Small, considered to be one of Notre Dame High's top returning players, 
has decided to forgo playing basketball to concentrate on a collegiate football 
career. 
</P>
<P>
"I'd really like to compete but I don't think the timing is right," said Small, 
an All-San Fernando Valley League tailback who is being recruited by several 
schools. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA113089-0019 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 141443 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 30, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 15A; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
