<DOCID> 141454 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 30, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 4; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
