</P>
<P>
CHILDREN TO HELP DECORATE CIVIC CENTER CHRISTMAS TREE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Civic Center Christmas tree will be decorated Dec. 14 and 15 when Long 
Beach schoolchildren hang their hand-made ornaments on the 14-foot fir tree, 
donated by Douglas Aircraft Co. Members of two barbershop quartets will sing 
