<HEADLINE>
<P>
WESTSIDE DIGEST: SANTA MONICA; 
</P>
<P>
BREAKFAST WITH SANTA CLAUS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The city Recreation Division will hold two separate breakfast sessions with 
Santa Claus on Dec. 16 at Memorial Park, 14th Street and Olympic Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
The $2 per person pancake breakfasts will be held from 8 to 10 a.m. and from 
10:30 a.m. to 12:30 p.m. Children under 8 must be accompanied by an adult. 
</P>
<P>
Tickets must be purchased in advance at the city recreation office at Clover 
Park, 2600 Ocean Park Blvd. Only 150 tickets will be sold for each session. 
</P>
</TEXT>
