<HEADLINE>
<P>
ROEMER OK AFTER SURGERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BATON ROUGE, La. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gov. Buddy Roemer successfully underwent surgery Wednesday to repair a small 
hernia, the governor's press office reported. Roemer was listed in good 
condition at an undisclosed Baton Rouge hospital following the 45-minute 
operation. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
