<P>
ACQUIRED IMMUNE DEFICIENCY SYNDROME; ART EXHIBITS; ARTISTS -- UNITED STATES; 
MEMORIALS; PERFORMANCE ARTISTS; MILLER, TIM; POLITICAL ACTIVISM 
</P>
