brothers who were shot and killed by soldiers Wednesday night for throwing 
stones at Israeli cars. 
</P>
<P>
In the occupied Gaza Strip, 12 Palestinians were shot and wounded by Israeli 
soldiers in stone-throwing clashes, hospital officials said. 
